      <title>前堪萨斯城联储主席霍尼格谈降息、美国债务和赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/former-kansas-city-fed-president-hoenig-on-rate-cuts-us-debt-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[堪萨斯城联邦储备银行前行长托马斯·霍尼格解释了为什么他认为现在说降息可能为时过早。他还在接受怀俄明州杰克逊霍尔的汤姆·基恩和丽莎·阿布拉莫维奇采访时讨论了美国债务和赤字问题。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/former-kansas-city-fed-president-hoenig-on-rate-cuts-us-debt-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 15:59:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储哈克谈降息“进程”和失业率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/fed-s-harker-on-process-of-rate-cuts-unemployment-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费城联邦储备银行行长帕特里克·哈克在讨论美国劳动力市场和经济对消费者的影响时表示，央行应该启动降息程序并“继续推进”。哈克在杰克逊霍尔经济研讨会间隙发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/fed-s-harker-on-process-of-rate-cuts-unemployment-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 15:50:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
