    <item>
      <title>开普敦获 IFC 1.58 亿美元贷款用于基础设施建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/cape-town-gets-158-million-ifc-loan-for-infrastructure-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非开普敦市从世界银行私人投资部门获得了 28 亿兰特（1.58 亿美元）的贷款，用于改善其供水、卫生设施和电力道路基础设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/cape-town-gets-158-million-ifc-loan-for-infrastructure-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 15:40:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储哈克认为失业不会带来巨大、过大的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/fed-s-harker-sees-no-large-outsized-risk-from-unemployment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费城联邦储备银行行长帕特里克·哈克表示，美国经济中存在两个消费者的故事，因为他认为失业不会带来重大经济风险。哈克在杰克逊霍尔经济研讨会间隙发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/fed-s-harker-sees-no-large-outsized-risk-from-unemployment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 15:31:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔强调降息理由 导致美元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/dovish-powell-adds-fuel-to-dollar-s-longest-plunge-in-16-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席鲍威尔确认央行下个月将降息的预期后，美元暴跌，引发主要全球货币上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/dovish-powell-adds-fuel-to-dollar-s-longest-plunge-in-16-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:44:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英镑兑美元升至两年多以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/pound-hits-strongest-level-in-over-two-years-against-us-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英镑攀升至两年多来的最高水平，进一步推动了英镑在全球范围的上涨，而上涨动力源于市场押注英国央行将比美联储更放松货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/pound-hits-strongest-level-in-over-two-years-against-us-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:09:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称美联储降息时机已到</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/powell-says-time-has-come-for-fed-to-cut-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，现在是下调关键政策利率的时候了，这肯定了官员们将于下个月开始降低借贷成本的预期，并明确表示他打算防止劳动力市场进一步降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/powell-says-time-has-come-for-fed-to-cut-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
